About:

    sumo, the SUpport MOdule manager, is a set of tools to support software
    development for the EPICS framework. It manages build dependencies and
    consistent builds of the EPICS base and EPICS support modules.

Author:
    Goetz Pfeiffer <Goetz.Pfeiffer@helmholtz-berlin.de>

Documentation:
    Documentation is in the directory "doc". You can read it by entering
    "file://<path-to-sumo>/doc/_build/index.html" as URL in your browser
    or you read the rst source, start with doc/index.rst.

Installation:

You may install sumo from source:

    See doc/sumo-install.rst for details.

